                                                                                                                                                             \
\cf5 \uc0\u9210 \cf0  Great question. Let me think through this systematically.                                                                                                  \
                                                                                                                                                             \
  
\f1\b Current order: Helmholtz \uc0\u8594  Teslameter (1-5 min later)
\f0\b0                                                                                                       \
   \
  - Arduino temp is synchronous with Helmholtz (good)                                                                                                        \
  - Teslameter probe temp is delayed, read when sample moves to the Teslameter rig                                                                         \
  - In a warming room, the Teslameter reads a temperature that is 
\f3\i later
\f0\i0  than the Helmholtz moment\
\
  
\f1\b What
\f0\b0  
\f1\b matters
\f0\b0  
